snippet.title: Reaction to Antphrodite's Reading on Summer Wells & Going over Robins Video to Reverend Donna 🔴
snippet.description:
So I am so happy to say that Antphrodite has gotten back to me and has given me permission to show this video and do my own reaction to it for y'all. 
Please make sure you check his channel out and subscribe 
https://youtube.com/c/antphrodite
BIG Thanks to him for allowing a smaller channel like mine to use his content and not want to strike us lol. He was very kind 😊  (fan-girling just a lil) lol 
So this Reading was done just over 4 months ago now. 
But I find it interesting what his cards were saying all that time ago.  And how it's really relating to the current situation that we on this platform and a.few others are really diving into.  
Cult OR Church?!?!   Y'all tell me.   Cause I'm only seeing CULT 👀 

🟪 ALSO TONIGHT 
We will react to the video that Robin sent Miss Reverend Donna and I'll read you the statement on that situation that Miss Reverend Donna shared with me to share with all of y'all.  She is so kind and doesn't deserve to be treated and called a creature and condemned to hell!  
And also a interview with the 3rd party that was helping set up that meeting with Robin and Miss Reverend Donna! 

🔴 * Conversations on this platform are just my thoughts and opinions and is being shared for entertainment purposes only and because I want some REAL answers on where the heck SUMMER WELLS is.
